text:
'Cuckservative' (definition): A conservative lost enough to be positively proud their leftist opponents aren't in jail (let alone executed or deported). 
Cuckservative mantra: "Better to lose than be beastly to the enemy."
John McCain was perhaps the ideal type.

The institutional playing-field isn't stacked against the Right. The Right is dumb and weak. 
The Left is playing annihilate the enemy, while the Right is playing coexistence. End that asymmetry and winning is entirely possible.
... Imagine running McCain and then Romney as presidential candidates and then complaining that the rules are stacked against you.
You don't think MAGA is exactly the Right rising to leftist levels of serious political hostility? (That's what it looks like to me.)
Quite. The idea of a legitimate leftist opposition is a mistake.
Pre-MAGA Republicans on the Democrats: "If they win we lose, but if we win it's a draw."
How McCain of you.
Generous. It sounds like some kind of Lamarckian nonsense to me.
Thankfully, the epoch we're entering will be extremely unsupportive of this leftist mind-control agenda.
People look at national media figures and think, understandably, that no one could possibly be worse.
Goldwater was the good timeline.
So it turns out you can just sue the Cathedral. msn.com/en-us/politics/gover…
Editor's note: "Shub-Niggurath was driven into bankruptcy and out of public life after being successfully sued for damages in a case that eventually reached the Supreme Court."
"'The situation is pretty gloomy,' Grimm said last month following the release of the Council’s annual analysis of the state of Germany’s economy." ... politico.eu/article/europe-e…
... Nominative determinism scripts the best miracles.
... "'The situation is pretty grim,' Gloomy said ..." as it's written in an alternative timeline quite simply isn't as good. We are blessed.
"The likely result [of Europe's impending economic crisis] is a radicalization of politics ... as populists on the far right and left seize the opportunity to attack the establishment."

LOL, no. That ultra-progressive froth is getting torched off at lightning speed. Democrats will be wielding the flame-thrower even more enthusiastically than the Republicans, because they know it's not even worth showing up for elections in woke clown costumes.
What choice will they have?

The 'rw theory' here is biorealism so basic it's hard to even spell it out without sounding like a special needs educator.
Soon.
